      "is_answer_order_important": false,
      "stimulus_html": "",
      "stem_html": "What is the stereochemistry of the pyruvate reduction shown in Figure 19.13? Does NADH lose its pro-<i>R</i> or pro-<i>S</i> hydrogen? Does addition occur to the Si face or Re face of pyruvate? (Review <b>Section 5.11</b>.)",
